<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM5.1">
<l>maṉṉu perumpukaḻ mātavaṉ māmaṇi vaṇṇaṉ maṇimuṭi maintaṉ</l>
<l>taṉṉai yukantatu kāraṇa mākaeṉ caṅkiḻak kumvaḻak kuṇṭē</l>
<l>puṉṉai kurukkatti ñāḻal ceruntip potumpiṉil vāḻuṅ kuyilē</l>
<l>paṉṉiyep pōtu miruntu virainteṉ pavaḷavā yaṉvarak kūvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it a custom that [I] should lose my bracelets for desiring Mādhava of enduring, great fame,</l>
<l>the great sapphire-hued [Lord], the Young Man with a crown [made of] gems?</l>
<l>O koel that lives in the hollows of the Champa trees, the Hiptage-creeper,</l>
<l rend="indent">Cassia and sedge trees!</l>
<l>Always uttering [His names], cry quickly so that my coral-lipped [Lord] comes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
